API Gateway
  Act as a guard for any request to web applications
  
Feature#1 
Separate out cross cutting concerns
-- Authentication
    Authentication is the process of identifying users and validating who they claim to be.
-- Authorization
    Authorization happens after a userâ€™s identity has been successfully authenticated.
    It is about offering full or partial access rights to resources like database, funds, and other critical information to get the job done.
-- SSL termination
-- DDoS protection / Throttling

Feature#2 
Seperate and consolidate cross cutting concerns across microservices
-- Routing 

Feature#3 
Replacing multiple client calls with single API call.
Some features of reverse proxy
-- Serving static content
-- Caching responses

Feature#4
Routing based on headers, paths and params etc.
Some features of load balancer component
-- Load Balancing
-- A/B testing
-- Canary release

Example
Self Managed
-- Apache
-- HAProxy
-- NGINX
-- Spring Cloud Gateway

Cloud Services
-- AWS API Gateway
-- Azure API Gateway
-- Google Cloud Endpoints
-- Apigee
